DESCRIPTION:Category: Events\nCome join us every 3rd Thursday of the month at 7pm!\n \nOur goal is to create safe spaces for queer\, trans and nonbinary climbers of color. These climb nights are run by queer people of color for queer people of color.\nhttps://portal.movementgyms.com/portland/programs/qtbipoc-climb-night?course=U2Vzc2lvbjoyMzc5NjE1MDY=&date=2026-08-20
DTEND:20260821T043000Z
