BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Category: Events\nThis group is a low-pressure talk space for climbers to share about our shared mental health journey. We chat. We climb. We connect. Led by Jonathan Morell\, LPC associate\, AMGA guide\, and Movement community member. For climbers 18+.\nhttps://portal.movementgyms.com/portland/programs/mental-health-talk-space?course=U2Vzc2lvbjoyNDI4ODg2NTI=&date=2026-09-07
DTEND:20260908T040000Z
LOCATION:Movement Portland
